precision mediump float;
uniform vec4 u_startColor;
uniform vec4 u_endColor;
uniform vec4 u_ColorTotal;
varying float linear;
varying vec2 v_texCoords;
uniform sampler2D u_texture;
void main()
{
  vec4 gradientColor = mix(u_startColor, u_endColor, clamp(linear, 0.0, 1.0));
  gl_FragColor = texture2D(u_texture, v_texCoords) * gradientColor * u_ColorTotal;
}]

  - String [attribute vec4 a_position;
attribute vec2 a_texCoord;
uniform mat4 u_projTrans;
uniform vec2 u_startPoint;
uniform vec2 u_endPoint;
varying float linear;
varying vec2 v_texCoords;
void main()
{
   vec2 a = u_endPoint - u_startPoint;
   vec2 b = vec2(a_position.x, a_position.y) - u_startPoint;
   float length1 = length(b * a / length(a));
   linear = length1 / length(a);
   v_texCoords = a_texCoord; 
   gl_Position =  u_projTrans * a_position;
}
]
  - String [attribute vec4 a_position;
uniform mat4 u_projTrans;
uniform vec2 u_startPoint;
uniform vec2 u_endPoint;
varying float linear;
void main()
{
   vec2 a = u_endPoint - u_startPoint;
   vec2 b = vec2(a_position.x, a_position.y) - u_startPoint;
   float length1 = length(b * a / length(a));
   linear = length1 / length(a);
   gl_Position =  u_projTrans * a_position;
}

uniform vec4 u_startColor;
uniform vec4 u_endColor;

attribute vec2 a_texCoord;
uniform mat4 u_projTrans;
uniform vec2 u_startPoint;
uniform vec2 u_endPoint;
varying float linear;
varying vec2 v_texCoords;
void main()
{
   vec2 a = u_endPoint - u_startPoint;
